text: Eunidia plagiata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Charles Joseph Gahan in 1898. It is known from Chad, Kenya, Zimbabwe, Mozambique, Ethiopia, South Africa, Botswana, and Tanzania.BioLib.cz - Eunidia plagiata.
